    m_Localized: How To Play
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 45033340477440
    m_Localized: 'Run, jump and slide your way through the factory to escape from
      the dangerous steam cloud behind you.

      Pick up gears along your way by
      running into them to enhance your abilities - if you collect all three gear
      types, you''ll unlock a temporary speed boost!

      See how far you can escape
      before you''re caught!


      A - Run backwards               D - Run forwards

      Space
      - Jump                          Esc - Pause'
